---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-sub">Bismillahirrahmanirrahim</div>
    <h1>Visi 2027/2028: Membangun Generasi Muslim Indonesia yang Kuat dalam Ilmu, Aqidah & Akhlak</h1>
    <div class="visi-box">
      Bersama lembaga pendidikan dan para pendidik, membangun generasi muslim Indonesia yang kuat dalam ilmu dan
      Aqidah Islamiyah, berwawasan global, dan berakhlakul karimah — bi idznillah.
    </div>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#buku" class="btn-utama">Lihat Katalog Buku</a>
      <a href="#reseller" class="btn-sekunder">Gabung Reseller</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* layer 1: foto background */
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/img-bg.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    filter: brightness(0.35) saturate(0.8);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* layer 2: gradient gelap di atas foto agar teks terbaca */
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(6,31,16,0.7) 0%, rgba(13,74,42,0.55) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    color: #f0e8c8;
  }
  .visi-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    line-height: 1.7;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-utama {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .btn-utama:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.26); }
  .btn-sekunder {
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-sekunder:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
</style>